<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>AI on Example Academy</title><link>https://meshery-extensions.github.io/digitalocean-academy/pr-preview/pr-85/tags/ai/</link><description>Recent content in AI on Example Academy</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en</language><atom:link href="https://meshery-extensions.github.io/digitalocean-academy/pr-preview/pr-85/tags/ai/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Certification Overview</title><link>https://meshery-extensions.github.io/digitalocean-academy/pr-preview/pr-85/learning-paths/3e2f9c82-1a4c-4781-adf9-99ec22cd994e/certified-ai-engineer/certification-overview/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://meshery-extensions.github.io/digitalocean-academy/pr-preview/pr-85/learning-paths/3e2f9c82-1a4c-4781-adf9-99ec22cd994e/certified-ai-engineer/certification-overview/</guid><description/></item><item><title>Designing AI Agents</title><link>https://meshery-extensions.github.io/digitalocean-academy/pr-preview/pr-85/learning-paths/3e2f9c82-1a4c-4781-adf9-99ec22cd994e/building-agentic-ai-with-gradient/designing-ai-agents/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://meshery-extensions.github.io/digitalocean-academy/pr-preview/pr-85/learning-paths/3e2f9c82-1a4c-4781-adf9-99ec22cd994e/building-agentic-ai-with-gradient/designing-ai-agents/</guid><description/></item><item><title>DigitalOcean Certified AI Engineer (DO-CAIE)</title><link>https://meshery-extensions.github.io/digitalocean-academy/pr-preview/pr-85/certifications/3e2f9c82-1a4c-4781-adf9-99ec22cd994e/digitalocean-certified-ai-engineer/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://meshery-extensions.github.io/digitalocean-academy/pr-preview/pr-85/certifications/3e2f9c82-1a4c-4781-adf9-99ec22cd994e/digitalocean-certified-ai-engineer/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;The &lt;strong&gt;DigitalOcean Certified AI Engineer (DO-CAIE)&lt;/strong&gt; is the DigitalOcean Academy&amp;rsquo;s flagship
credential. It validates that you can take an AI application from idea to production on DigitalOcean&amp;rsquo;s
AI-Native Cloud — building grounded, agentic applications on the
&lt;a href="https://docs.digitalocean.com/products/gradient-ai-platform/"&gt;Gradient AI Platform&lt;/a&gt;, serving models
on GPU infrastructure, and operating it all with &lt;a href="https://meshery.io/"&gt;Meshery&lt;/a&gt; on
&lt;a href="https://docs.digitalocean.com/products/kubernetes/"&gt;DigitalOcean Kubernetes&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h2 id="how-you-earn-it" class="heading-link"&gt;
 How you earn it
 &lt;a href="#how-you-earn-it" class="heading-anchor" aria-label="Permalink to this heading"&gt;🔗&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The credential has two required parts:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A &lt;strong&gt;written exam&lt;/strong&gt; — 60 multiple-choice and scenario questions across the seven domains above
(90 minutes, proctored). Pass mark &lt;strong&gt;70%&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A &lt;strong&gt;hands-on capstone&lt;/strong&gt; — an end-to-end agentic application served on GPU infrastructure and
operated with Meshery, graded against a published rubric.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Both the exam and the capstone are delivered as the
&lt;a href="https://cloud.layer5.io/academy/challenges/3e2f9c82-1a4c-4781-adf9-99ec22cd994e/docaie-certification-exam/"&gt;DO-CAIE Certification Exam challenge&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>GPU Droplets Fundamentals</title><link>https://meshery-extensions.github.io/digitalocean-academy/pr-preview/pr-85/learning-paths/3e2f9c82-1a4c-4781-adf9-99ec22cd994e/gpu-compute-and-model-serving/gpu-droplets-fundamentals/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://meshery-extensions.github.io/digitalocean-academy/pr-preview/pr-85/learning-paths/3e2f9c82-1a4c-4781-adf9-99ec22cd994e/gpu-compute-and-model-serving/gpu-droplets-fundamentals/</guid><description/></item><item><title>Meshery Fundamentals for AI Platform Engineers</title><link>https://meshery-extensions.github.io/digitalocean-academy/pr-preview/pr-85/learning-paths/3e2f9c82-1a4c-4781-adf9-99ec22cd994e/cloud-native-ai-with-meshery/meshery-fundamentals-for-ai/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://meshery-extensions.github.io/digitalocean-academy/pr-preview/pr-85/learning-paths/3e2f9c82-1a4c-4781-adf9-99ec22cd994e/cloud-native-ai-with-meshery/meshery-fundamentals-for-ai/</guid><description/></item><item><title>Orientation</title><link>https://meshery-extensions.github.io/digitalocean-academy/pr-preview/pr-85/learning-paths/3e2f9c82-1a4c-4781-adf9-99ec22cd994e/ai-foundations-on-digitalocean/ai-native-cloud/overview/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://meshery-extensions.github.io/digitalocean-academy/pr-preview/pr-85/learning-paths/3e2f9c82-1a4c-4781-adf9-99ec22cd994e/ai-foundations-on-digitalocean/ai-native-cloud/overview/</guid><description/></item><item><title>The DigitalOcean AI-Native Cloud</title><link>https://meshery-extensions.github.io/digitalocean-academy/pr-preview/pr-85/learning-paths/3e2f9c82-1a4c-4781-adf9-99ec22cd994e/ai-foundations-on-digitalocean/ai-native-cloud/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 00